logical operators:
 juts another set of symbols that we can use to combine multiple boolean values. there are logical operators
 ! &&

 NOT Operators
    Not is used to negate the boolean values if something is true it will make it false if something is false it will
    make it true.

Rules that we should fallow:
1)we can only use byte short int char string in switch case statements
2)we cant use relational operators in switch case statements are also not allowed
3) we cant use logical operators